data.description: Welcome to this charming Cape with an updated, spacious and permitted 1 bedroom family accessory dwelling unit in desirable North Andover! This 3-bed, 2 bath home is perfect for multi-generational living or expansion. Step inside to a warm & inviting atmosphere with a bright living room featuring a fireplace & hardwood floors flowing throughout the bedrooms and dining room. The kitchen offers ample cabinetry and plenty of space for an eat-in table or breakfast nook. Two generously sized bedrooms a modern bathroom and dining room with sliders to the covered back deck complete the main floor. You will find easy access from the garage to both the first floor and accessory dwelling unit where you will find a lovely small kitchen, comfortable living area, cozy bedroom, and full bathroom. Located near top-rated schools, parks, and shopping, & easy access to major highways. Don't miss the opportunity to own this versatile Cape. Showings start at the Open House Sat. 7/15 & Sun. 7/16 11-1 pm
